→ Inquiries of employees and inspection of documents concerning the sustainability strategy, sustainability principles and sustainability management including the stakeholder dialog of Siemens AG,

→ Inquiries of management and relevant employees involved in the preparation of the report about the prepa- ration process, about the internal control system related to this process, and about disclosures in the report,

→ Inquiries of employees responsible for data capture and consolidation, about the data capture and compilation methods as well as internal controls to the extent relevant for the assurance of the disclosures in the report,